## Embed Ready

Each demo is a single HTML file, zero dependencies (except Three.js CDN for 3D ones). Embed via:
```html
<iframe src="https://superinstance.github.io/cocapn-ai-web/demo-narrows.html" 
        style="width:100%;height:600px;border:none;border-radius:12px;">
</iframe>
```

